OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start for many,
OL,6,Falthough low cloud quickly burning
OL,7,Faway through the morning. A fine day
OL,8,Ffollows with warm sunny spells, but
OL,9,Falso some patchy higher cloud. Some
OL,10,Flower cloud perhaps persisting along
OL,11,FLincolnshire coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWinds easing to become mainly
OL,14,Flight, and while some low cloud is
OL,15,Flikely to spill inland, many southern
OL,16,Fand western parts could stay cloud-
OL,17,Ffree.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
