OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSimilar to Thursday, with any
OL,6,Fcloud clearing through the morning, to
OL,7,Fgive good sunny spells. Perhaps a
OL,8,Ftouch cooler than recent days, with a
OL,9,Flight north to northeasterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,12,Fand dry, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,13,Fand likely staying clearer overnight.
OL,14,FCooler than recent days with
OL,15,Ftemperatures easing to nearer normal
OL,16,Ffor mid-July.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
